name: Senka Adonis - Zhou Gong
desc: You can target 1 Continuous Spell/Trap you control; send that card to the GY, and if you do, add 1 "Senka" Spell/Trap from your Deck to your hand. If your other "Senka" monster's effect is activated: You can target 1 monster your opponent controls; negate its effects for the rest of the turn. You can only use each effect of "Senka Adonis - Zhou Gong" once per turn.
